<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}} - AIRLINE Reservation System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>AIRLINE Reservation System</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">홈</a>
            <a href="/admin">관리자</a>
            <a href="/user">사용자</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <h2>관리자 페이지</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
            <div>
                <h3>공항 관리</h3>
                <p>총 {{airports.length}}개 공항</p>
                <a href="/admin/airport" class="btn">관리하기</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>항공기 관리</h3>
                <p>총 {{airplanes.length}}대 항공기</p>
                <a href="/admin/airplane" class="btn">관리하기</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>항공편 관리</h3>
                <p>총 {{flights.length}}개 항공편</p>
                <a href="/admin/flight" class="btn">관리하기</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <h3>빠른 메뉴</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/admin/airport">공항 관리</a></li>
                <li><a href="/admin/airplane">항공기 관리</a></li>
                <li><a href="/admin/flight">항공편 관리</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 AIRLINE Reservation System</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

